title: Back home, Blue Jays break out to beat Royals 11-8 in Game 3
text:
> Top News Back home, Blue Jays break out to beat Royals 11-8 in Game 3 Toronto Blue Jays starting pitcher Marcus Stroman reacts after a pitch against the Kansas City Royals during the sixth inning in Game 3 of baseball's American League Championship Series on Monday, Oct. 19, 2015, in Toronto. (Frank Gunn/The Canadian Press via AP) MANDATORY CREDIT The most compelling, sharable stories from across the web.
